author: concelvio
msg: Whit this commit the point "* kres/jersey module should not have dependency to kres/owlapi in any way" can be checked out.
- renamed artifact from org.apache.stanbol.owlapi to org.apache.stanbol.owl; renamed single packages;
- moved OWLOtnologyWriter.java from org.apache.stanbol.kres.jersey.writer to org.apache.stanbol.owl.web;
- removed OWLmodelWriter.java from org.apache.stanbol.kres.jersey.writer (not used any more);
- refactoring where required imports and dependency in pom.xml files.
